Booktitle = {PROCEEDINGS OF THE NINETEENTH INTERNATIONAL SYMPOSIUM ON IMPROVEMENT OF
   ORNAMENTAL PLANTS: BREEDING ORNAMENTALS IN THE FUTURE: GOALS, GENES,
   TOOLS},
